      <article class="styleguide-content">
        <p id="intro">This is <a href="https://www.github.com/dosomething/forge">Forge</a>, our interface framework and pattern library. It defines a set of base styles and common patterns shared throughout our website. It's a strong foundation for building beautiful interfaces.</p>

        <p>Forge was built for our internal needs at DoSomething.org, but it could also work for your organization. Feel free to fork our <a href="https://github.com/dosomething/forge">GitHub repository</a> and use it as a starting point for your own pattern library, or read more about why we <a href="https://blog.dosomething.org/we-open-sourced-our-code-heres-why-you-should-too/">open-source our code</a>.</p>

        <h2 id="base">Base Styles</h2>
        <p>Content is the basis for our design, so we need a strong typographic foundation. We define base HTML classes with comfortable font-size and spacing for readability, and a clear information hierarchy between elements.</p>

        <%- include('pattern', { pattern: styleguide.section('Base - Inline Elements') }) %>

        <h3 id="fonts-and-colors">Fonts &amp; Colors</h3>
        <p>We use <a href="http://www.marksimonson.com/fonts/view/proxima-nova">Proxima Nova</a> for all headings and body copy.</p>
        <p class="font-tile" style="font-family: 'Proxima Nova'; font-weight: 400; ">
          Any cause, anytime, anywhere. <code>($font-proxima-nova, $weight-normal)</code>
        </p>

        <p class="font-tile" style="font-family: 'Proxima Nova'; font-weight: 600; ">
          Any cause, anytime, anywhere. <code>($font-proxima-nova, $weight-sbold)</code>
        </p>

        <p class="font-tile" style="font-family: 'Proxima Nova'; font-weight: 700; ">
          Any cause, anytime, anywhere. <code>($font-proxima-nova, $weight-bold)</code>
        </p>

        <p>We use <a href="https://www.google.com/fonts/specimen/Covered+By+Your+Grace">Covered By Your Grace</a> as the "voice" of DoSomething.org.</p>
        <p class="font-tile" style="font-family: 'CoveredGrace';">
          Any cause, anytime, anywhere. <code>($font-handwritten, $weight-normal)</code>
        </p>

        <p>We have three primary brand colors.</p>
        <ul class="gallery -duo">
          <li>
            <div class="color-tile" data-hex="#23b7fb">
              <strong>Blue</strong>
              <code>($blue) <span class="color-tile__value js-color-label">&hellip;</span></code>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <div class="color-tile" data-hex="#4e2b63">
