              <strong>Yellow</strong>
              <code>($yellow) <span class="color-tile__value js-color-label">&hellip;</span></code>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>For consistency, we try to use these four grayscale values throughout our interfaces.</p>
        <ul class="gallery -duo">
          <li>
            <div class="color-tile" data-hex="#222">
